{"type": "article", "id": 7455, "title": "Raul Lemesoff 《集体教学武器》", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-17T07:45:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234129F6wSkjBY1thV7ZmK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t世界读书日临近，7UP 与布宜诺斯艾利斯艺术家 Raul Lemesoff 合作设计了作品《集体教学武器》（Weapon Of Mass Instruction），这个看似是坦克的装置，其真身其实是一个流动图书馆。这个“坦克”由一辆 1979 年的古董车改造而成，里面摆放了 900 多本小说，传记等作品。艺术家开着它穿梭在城市里面，为人们发放免费的图书。而拿到书的唯一条件就是把书看完。 Raul Lemesoff 希望借此唤醒人们的读书意识，用知识的武器武装自己，扛起传递知识的责任。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052341272L1AFS7YbxTpHBng.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71271394\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234127mcQIUXvb71EBxkGO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64425428\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234128TBDXMv29wbryxSkn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68337408\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052341280l9broqy63AtYLHv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62713936\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234128dygiZCnURQhAXSmV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71515892\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234129gM6nPoEJwNOlCjYk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"wi